stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unregistered
    
    Unregistered --> Pending: Submit Registration
    Pending --> Registered: Transaction Confirmed
    
    Registered --> Unverified: Initial State
    Unverified --> VerificationPending: Request Verification
    VerificationPending --> Verified: Approved by Admins
    VerificationPending --> Unverified: Rejected
    
    Verified --> Active: Health Check Passed
    Active --> Degraded: Performance Issues
    Degraded --> Active: Issues Resolved
    Active --> Offline: No Response
    Offline --> Active: Comes Back Online
    
    Active --> Maintenance: Scheduled Downtime
    Maintenance --> Active: Maintenance Complete
    
    Verified --> UpdatePending: Metadata Update Request
    UpdatePending --> Verified: Update Approved
    UpdatePending --> Verified: Update Rejected
    
    Registered --> Transferred: NFT Transfer
    Transferred --> Registered: New Owner
    
    Registered --> Burned: Destroy NFT
    Burned --> [*]
    
    note right of Active
        Normal operational state
        Handling encryption requests
    end note
    
    note right of Degraded
        Slow response times
        High error rates
        Partial functionality
    end note
    
    note right of Offline
        Not responding to health checks
        Automatic alerts triggered
    end note